re as real as you and friendships will far outlast EQ, hence joining an online game, meeting people from all over the world and having FUN! Equipment I soloed will go, friends I grouped with won't. <br /> <br />NOW GET OUT THERE AND HAVE SOME FUN, IT'S A GAME! <br /> <br />PS please ensure that when drinking you warn your comrades in arms:) <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Tue Sep 21 15:03:20 2004 by Steinhound</span></i></p>
